'''''The Arts Council Collection of Modern Literary Manuscripts 1963-1972''''' is a catalogue of manuscripts collected by the [[Wikipedia:Arts Council of Great Britain|Arts Council of Great Britain]] (through its National Manuscript Collection of Contemporary Writers), acquired mainly by the [[Wikipedia:British Museum|British Museum]].

A [[Letter to Elizabeth Jennings|letter from J.R.R. Tolkien to Elizabeth Jennings]] is illustrated in plate 3.
